summary: An ordinance providing for the improvement of 34th Ave. Southwest from Southwest Brandon Street to Southwest Juneau Street; and certain other streets, avenues and alleys; by constructing sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same; all in accordance with Resolution No. 18680 of the City Council of the City of Seattle, creating a local improvement district therefor, and providing that payment for said improvement be made by special assessments upon property in said district payable by the mode of installment notes.
